/*
   This JavaScript contains the text that the HTML files will display in their "pop-up text boxes"
   This file is CASE SENSITIVE, both the HTML document and this script must have the exact variable
   names in order for this to work.
   At runtime, when an HTML document comes up with an error that involves a ;  chances are
   an "=" sign is missing, there are quotes within quotes or there is a character outside of 
   a set of quotes.
*/


